Feature: V7 P2 T3 weekly operating governance
  As cross-functional leadership
  We want a weekly operating governance cadence
  So that risk decisions are auditable and execution remains stable

  Scenario: Weekly governance protocol is approved
    Given churn runbook parity is completed
    And governance board sections and ownership are defined
    And weekly risk review uses a severity rubric and escalation rules
    And weekly closure produces auditable commitments
    When evidence is consolidated for V7-P2-T3
    Then V7-P2-T3 is accepted
    And evidence is published in "docs/validation/V7_P2_T3_WEEKLY_OPERATING_GOVERNANCE.json"
